Filled bar chart: The above two charts show the educational attainment by race in Santa Clara county (CA) for individuals 25 and older. In this particular county, there are a disproportionate number of individuals who self-identify as Asian alone with Bachelors degrees, compared to the number of individuals of other races with bachelors degrees. Since this data is only for those 25 and up, these stats may change as current students graduate.
